# 文件功能：限制平台容器构建上下文，避免把本地依赖、缓存、日志和 Runtime 私有源码打进镜像。

.agents/
.codex/
.git/
.github/
.pytest_cache/

**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyd
**/*.so
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.venv/
**/venv/

**/node_modules/
**/.pnpm-store/
**/.npm/
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

*.log
logs/
editor-vite-*.log
editor-vite-*.err.log
playwright-report/
test-results/

.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
backend/.env
backend/.env.*
!backend/.env.example
!backend/.env.*.example

backend/build_artifacts/
backend/data/

runtime/*
!runtime/src/
runtime/src/*
!runtime/src/runtime-kit/
runtime/src/runtime-kit/*
!runtime/src/runtime-kit/manifest/
runtime/src/runtime-kit/manifest/*
!runtime/src/runtime-kit/manifest/runtime-kit.manifest.json
